name: Night-Soarer

NIGHT-SOARER
PNG file, 2953 x 4724 px (300 dpi)

first collection for "DRAGON STAMP" series.

"a mystical dragon. It has silver-black scales, ridges on its back with exceptionally large wings to fly in the night-sky. Its breath is a cloud of gas that puts most beings to sleep. It lives underneath a series of standing stones with medium-sized hoard and consists of almost entirely magical artifacts"
